---
title: Honey and Thyme Root Veg Carrots and Parsnips Glazed with Honey and Thyme
description: Root veg naturally caramelises when roasted, so a drizzling of honey is just the thing to draw out their sweetness, while thyme - with its more earthy tones - blends beautifully to create a wholesome side to your Christmas centrepiece.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/maple-and-thyme-root-vegetables-a01ede3c.jpg
